properties.Name: EquifaxCompanyFinancialAccountRecent36Months
properties.Description: The details of financial accounts for the recent 36 months.

Columns.Name: EfxId
Columns.Description: The EFX ID™ is a unique and persistent nine-digit number that identifies and tracks the business unit with which you have the credit relationship;

Columns.Name: ProfileTimestamp
Columns.Description:
Provides the timestamp when the inquiry was made as recorded
by Equifax (Eastern Time).

Columns.Name: EquifaxFinancialAccountTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Financial Account Type.

Columns.Name: DateOpened
Columns.Description: Date Opened refers to the date on which the specific credit obligation was initiated.

Columns.Name: DateReported
Columns.Description: Date Reported refers to the most recent data submission received from the contributing data source.

Columns.Name: DateClosed
Columns.Description: Date account was reported closed.

Columns.Name: OriginalCreditLimitAmount
Columns.Description: Highest credit reported/original loan amount/original credit limit.

Columns.Name: HighCreditAmount
Columns.Description: Highest credit reported/original loan amount/original credit limit.

Columns.Name: OriginalLoanAmount
Columns.Description: Highest credit reported/original loan amount/original credit limit.

Columns.Name: CurrentCreditLimitAmount
Columns.Description: Current Credit Limit: Current credit limit reported.

Columns.Name: BalanceAmount
Columns.Description: Balance: Total reported balance, including any past due amount.

Columns.Name: PastDueAmount
Columns.Description: Total amount past due from each aging category.

Columns.Name: 24MonthHistory
Columns.Description:
The 24-month grid contains consecutive payment performance indicators for the 24 months prior to the payment date. The far left position in the grid represents the previous month's overall account payment status, continuing in monthly increments from left to right for the entire 24-month period. 

The grid provides a convenient recap of historical payment performance for each of the business's accounts.

Columns.Name: ActiveAccountIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the account is active.

Columns.Name: MaturityExpirationDate
Columns.Description: The maturity expiration date of the account.

Columns.Name: PaymentAmount
Columns.Description: The payment amount.

Columns.Name: LastPaymentAmount
Columns.Description: The last payment amount.

Columns.Name: LastPaymentDate
Columns.Description: The last payment date.

Columns.Name: SecuredIndicator
Columns.Description:
Indicates that the account is secured.

Ex:
- Secured

Columns.Name: NumberOfGuarantors
Columns.Description: The number of guarantors.

Columns.Name: GovernmentGuaranteedIndicator
Columns.Description: Indicates that the account is government guaranteed.

Columns.Name: EquifaxFinancialAccountStatusTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Financial Account Status Type.

Columns.Name: EquifaxPaymentTypeId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of an Equifax Payment Type.
